---
import Prose from "@components/Prose.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="Now | Hyun Don Moon"
  pageDescription="What I'm up to right now"
>
  <Prose>
    <h1>Now</h1>

    <p>
      This page is inspired by Derek Sivers' <a
        href="https://nownownow.com/about"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">/now pages</a
      > movement. It's a simple concept: a page that tells you what someone is focused
      on at this point in their life.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h3>November, 2025</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Work & Learning</strong>: I completed a major Electron version upgrade for our company's messenger app and have been diving into AI tools like Claude Code to improve my workflow. I also met up with former colleagues to talk about our careers as front-end developers.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Reading</strong>: I'm completely engrossed in Robin Hobb's Farseer Trilogy and am currently on the third book, <em>Assassin's Quest</em>.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Gaming</strong>: I just borrowed <em>The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild</em> from the company library and am looking forward to starting it.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Personal</strong>: I spent the Chuseok holiday with my parents and helped harvest persimmons and sweet potatoes on my uncle's farm in Kunsan. I also had a surprise reunion with a friend from my military service.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:2em; font-size:0.9em; color: #666;">
        This page was updated automatically using n8n & Google Gemini.
      </p>
    </section>
  </Prose>
</BaseLayout>